race.comment: RATTLE'N'ROLL (6) resumes. Three runs last time in were good in some handy maidens that look largely stronger than what he faces here. Third to Surfin' Bird when fresh at Moe last time in is excellent form for this and with even luck from the gate he should go close. TOPMOST (7) resumes. He's another who's had a few chances but is largely consistent, only missing a place once which came on very heavy going at Sale before a spell. Draws better than the main danger and that could prove key. LOWESTOFT (10) resumes having shown glimpses last time in. This may be short of her best trip but she can run a good race. THE SECRET (13) resumes. She has pieces of form that say a maiden win won't be too far away.
